<h2>Small Groups</h2><p class="highlight">Doing life together:</p><ul class="link_block"><li><a href="#Working">Working Women</a><a href="/ministries/children/kids-summer-experience/"></a></li><li><a href="#shawl">Prayer Shawl</a></li><li><a href="#deborah">Deborah Ministry</a></li><li><a href="#prayer">Women's Prayer Circle</a></li></ul><hr><h3><a id="deborah"></a>Deborah Group</h3><hr><p><strong>Days:</strong> 1st and 3rd Thursday of the month<br><strong>Time:</strong> 9:30 AM<br><strong>Location:</strong> Fireside Room<br><strong>Leader:</strong> Jan Rasmussen</p><p>If you like to quilt or sew, come at 9:30 AM to join this fun group of women using their talents for ministry! The quilts are donated to various charities (My Father's House, Portland Rescue Mission, House of Ruth, Salvation Army, etc). Sewing projects include making pajamas for those using the services of Portland Rescue Mission, sewing concert dresses for our Children's Choir, and other projects as needed.</p><p><strong>(This group meets every month, September-May, with the exception of December, when they meet the first week only.)</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><hr><h3><a id="Working"></a>Working Women</h3><hr><h4><img src="http://www.pcctoday.com/monkimage.php?mediaDirectory=mediafiles&amp;mediaId=2275827&amp;fileName=graphic--women--a-confident-heart-swope-0-0-150-232.jpg" width="150" height="232" alt="GRAPHIC : WOMEN : A Confident Heart, Swope" title="GRAPHIC : WOMEN : A Confident Heart, Swope" style="vertical-align: top; margin-left: 10px; margin-right: 10px;"></h4><h4>A CONFIDENT Heart by Renee Swope</h4><p>Do you ever feel like you&rsquo;re not good enough, smart enough, or valuable enough? Do words you say to yourself, or hear from others, make you question your worth and purpose? Even with a great family, a successful career, and/or a thriving ministry, we can sometimes struggle with paralyzing self-doubt.</p><p>Taking a chapter a month out of A Confident Heart by Renee Swope we will....as a group of professional women...drink coffee, share, pray, laugh, cry, talk about work-life-relationships, study the Bible, apply God's Word and...</p><ul><li>Learn to fail forward even when life or sin sets you back</li><li>Live confidently in your God-given purpose, passion, and personality</li><li>Break free from people-pleasing and performance-based living</li><li>Exchange &ldquo;against me&rdquo; thoughts with scripture-based God is &ldquo;for me&rdquo; thoughts</li><li>Trust the certainty of God&rsquo;s promises in the uncertainty of your circumstances and emotions</li></ul><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.pcctoday.com" target="_blank" class="button" style="text-align: center;">Register for Working Women Small Group</a></p><table border="0"><tbody><tr><td><strong>Day</strong></td><td><strong>Dates</strong></td><td><strong>Time</strong></td><td><strong>Location</strong></td><td><strong>Cost</strong></td></tr><tr><td>TBD</td><td>&nbsp;Fall 2013</td><td>TBD</td><td>TBD</td><td>(book price)</td></tr></tbody></table><p>This group is still forming. Contact <script type='text/javascript'>var u733689285='lnoah'; var h4687628='pcctoday.com';var linktext='Linda Noah';h4687628='pcctoday.com';document.write('<a href=' + 'mail' + 'to:' + u733689285 + '@' + h4687628 + '>' + linktext + '</a>');
